Approach Comparison
| Approach                  | Data Structure | Time         | Space  |
| ------------------------- | -------------- | ------------ | ------ |
| Brute Force               | None           | `O(nk)`      | `O(1)` |
| Max Heap                  | PriorityQueue  | `O(n log k)` | `O(k)` |
| Monotonic Deque (Optimal) | Deque          | `O(n)`       | `O(k)` |

Pattern Recognition
Type: Fixed Size Sliding Window.
Special Technique: Monotonic Queue (Deque).
Key Insight: Maintain elements in decreasing order so that the front is always the maximum of the current window.
